# =============================================================================
# PROPRIETARY SOLUTIONS — never commit company-specific solutions to this repo
# =============================================================================
# The Sage framework is MIT-licensed. Solutions may have different licenses.
# Company/customer solutions must live in their own private repositories and
# be mounted at runtime via the SAGE_SOLUTIONS_DIR environment variable.
#
# Pattern: any solutions/<name>/ folder that is NOT one of the maintained
# open examples is excluded here.
# =============================================================================
solutions/dfs/
solutions/customer_*/
solutions/private_*/
solutions/proprietary_*/

